  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to determine the diagnostic accuracy of SURECardio CT-FFR to detect
      functionally significant coronary stenosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      CT acquision and invasive FFR measurement is performed for each patients. The diagnostic
      accuracy of coronary CTA and SURECardio CT-FFR is investigated using Invasive FFR is used as
      the reference standard.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
